data.description: 21.27 acres with incredible views to include Elk and all other wildlife at your front and back door!  7 Bedrooms with walk-in-closets & 4 bath detitled home that is installed on a stick built basement built on-site.  Located minutes from Anaconda, MT and The Big Hole River with premiere blue-ribbon trout fishing!  1st floor has an open concept with a large living room, dining room, and kitchen.  Off the kitchen is a laundry room, sink, and plenty of storage.  2 bedrooms and a full bathroom and a private master suite with bathroom, walk-in closet, and bonus room you can use as an office.   Basement includes a large game room, movie room, 2 bedrooms with a Jack and Jill bathroom, & 2 more large bedrooms and 1 full bath with a Sauna you can finish.  Experience ultimate comfort with radiant heated flooring in the basement and garage.  Wood burning stove in the oversize 2-car garage, providing ample room for storage to include a workshop equipped with 220V outlet, and a loft with a workout room.  Private courtyard nestled in the aspen trees where you will find a path leading to an outdoor entertainment area with a wooden pavilion, a bbq area, and horseshoe pit.  Electricity to the home with off-grid solar backup.
